        {
            "title": "黃大仙茶餐廳油煙槽起火冒煙 消防迅速救熄 約20街坊一度自行到疏散",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9cd07815c152ca32052c9883dbfdcf4e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022206570517456.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>黃大仙發生火警。今日清晨5時許，毓華里22號地下一間「天馬茶餐廳」廚房冒煙，消防接獲多人報案，派員到場後迅速將火撲熄。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場消息指，事發時茶餐廳剛開舖準備營業，懷疑油煙槽起火，消防從側門進入開喉救熄，毋須疏散居民。不過據悉，附近一間老人院約20人一度自行戶外暫避，火勢控制後全數返回老人院，並無造成驚擾。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096405/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06efe01018498f4a9a7a02ef633f7028/2025-02/17_0_5.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096406/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee4831547b24a4ef0d4c826cb22dc1c3/2025-02/12_17.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4096407/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a7faac295a3d17db1b5f6c0201f3e29/2025-02/13_16.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054232/即時-港聞-黃大仙茶餐廳油煙槽起火冒煙-消防迅速救熄-約20街坊一度自行到疏散",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 07:02:12",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "15歲仔釣魚誤墮大埔林村河 消防游繩救回上岸",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3ef7527418100f5c921a06a9042e605f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022206323749067.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大埔發生墮河事故。昨日（21日）晚上8時許，一名15歲少年在林村河近天橋位置釣魚，其間魚竿不慎誤墮河中，少年遂沿斜坡希望拾回魚竿，不料跌入河中，無法自行上岸，惟有報警求助。\n\n</p>\n<p>網上流傳相關影片，一名消防員游繩，為少年縛好繩索，少年抓緊繩索，自行走上斜坡，再由其他站在行人路的消防員將他拉回路面。少年沒有受傷，無需送院。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054231/即時-港聞-15歲仔釣魚誤墮大埔林村河-消防游繩救回上岸",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 06:41:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
